"suffit de vous rendre sur"

#. module: summer_camps
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:summer_camps.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Generate a public share link</strong> for each template that can be "
"reused."
msgstr ""
"<strong>Générez un lien de partage public</strong> pour chaque modèle afin "
"de pouvoir le réutiliser."

#. module: summer_camps
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:summer_camps.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Insert the share link directly into your confirmation emails</"
"strong> so parents can sign the document easily before arrival."
msgstr ""
"<strong>Insérez le lien de partage directement dans vos e-mails de "
"confirmation</strong> pour permettre aux parents de signer facilement le "
"document avant l’arrivée."

#. module: summer_camps
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:summer_camps.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Integrated \"Register Now\" buttons</strong> link to event "
"registration."
msgstr ""
"<strong>Des boutons intégrés \"S’inscrire maintenant\"</strong> redirigent "
"vers l’inscription à l’événement."

#. module: summer_camps
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:summer_camps.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Let customers self-schedule</strong> discovery calls or info "
